replies.body:
For support questions, I have knowledge about a wide area of issues so I can help everyone out!  Kind of like Kayle it's good to be a jack of all trades, but there are specialists like our tech team who can take this support to the next level!  I don't speak for other teams beyond player support, so developer questions are best left up to their field of expertise.  

I'm always learning something new from friends around me and players who post here.  For example players were having some issues with crashing recently, and with investigating and troubleshooting it turned out to be a result of third party programs.  Pieces of information like this from the community has helped me and other folks out!  I'm not here to throw around a rulebook, but to help and spread goodwill!  And poro snax!  {{item:2010}} 

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
